      "en": "Create a new Snapshot instance with a filtered traces sequence, filters is a list of DomainFilter and Filter instances. If filters is an empty list, return a new Snapshot instance with a copy of the traces. All inclusive filters are applied at once, a trace is ignored if no inclusive filters match it. A trace is ignored if at least one exclusive filter matches it. Changed in version 3.6: DomainFilter instances are now also accepted in filters."
